'''斜紋小劃蝽'''([[學名|學名]]:'''''Micronecta scholtzi''''')是一種常見於[[歐洲|歐洲]]淡水池塘與湖泊的[[劃蝽科|劃蝽科]]成員。成蟲體長約2毫米，頭部、前胸背板與雄性生殖器帶有獨特的斜線深色花紋。
<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.snl.lu/publications/bulletin/SNL_2006_106_063_066.pdf |title=''Micronecta scholtzi'' (Fieber, 1860) new to Luxembourg. With new records of three other rare aquatic heteropteran species (Insecta, Heteroptera) |journal=Bulletin de la Société des naturalistes luxembourgeois |volume=106 |year=2006 |pages=63–65 |author=Raoul Gerend |access-date=2020-09-29 |archive-date=2017-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101095638/http://www.snl.lu/publications/bulletin/SNL_2006_106_063_066.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[File:Micronecta_scholtzi_-_bottom.jpg|left]]
雄性斜紋小劃蝽會透過摩擦腹部與生殖器上的特殊突起結構發聲求偶。該聲音的傳播距離最遠僅50微米，但音量卻異常驚人，與該物種的嬌小體型不成比例。根據一支由[[法國|法國]]和[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]][[生物學家|生物學家]]和[[音訊工程師|音訊工程師]]組成的研究團隊記錄，雄性斜紋小劃蝽的求偶音音量高達99.2[[分貝|分貝]]，與大型貨運車的行進噪音相當。
<ref name="loud">{{Cite journal|author1=Sueur, Jérôme |author2=Mackie, David |author3=Windmill, James F. C.  |lastauthoramp=yes |year=2011|title=So Small, So Loud: Extremely High Sound Pressure Level from a Pygmy Aquatic Insect (Corixidae, Micronectinae)|journal=PLOS ONE|volume=6|issue=6|page=e21089|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0021089|pmc=3115974|pmid=21698252}}</ref>
[[金氏世界紀錄|金氏世界紀錄]]將其評為「世上最吵的陰莖」，斜紋小劃蝽也因此成為「世上最吵的動物」。
<ref>[http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/100677-loudest-penis Loudest penis] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/100677-loudest-penis |date=20201216090510 }}:<br/>"The loudest penis is that of a tiny European species of aquatic freshwater insect. ''Micronecta scholtzi'' is a very small water boatman, just 2 mm long, but when it rubs its penis against its abdomen the chirping noise created can be up to 99.2 decibels."</ref>
學者認為關於斜紋小劃蝽發聲機制的研究，將有助於[[超音波|超音波]]科技的發展。
